description: Demolition of existing 2 no residential blocks and construction of 42 units.  Dickenson House: Redevelopemt to provide part 3/part 4/ part 5  storey building comprising 14 x one bed , 9 x two bed, 6 x three bed and 1 x four bed residential units. Erection of 7 houses in 2 x 2 storey terraced blocks consisting of 1 x four and 6 x three bed houses.   Womersley House: Redevelopment to provide 1 x 4 storey block fronting Womersley Road, N8 comprising 3 x one bed, 1 x two bed and 1 x three bed residential units. Provision of 34 car parking spaces, cycle storage and landscaping.
